    <body style="background-color: white; padding: 10px;">
        <h1>Display a preview in the traceability diagram</h1>
        &lt;p&gt;The preview in the traceability diagram enables you to display detailed information about a node.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;Follow these steps if you want to display detailed information about a node. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Open an asset page.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click &lt;strong&gt;Traceability &amp;gt; Diagram&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Select a node.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;On the diagram toolbar, click &lt;img class=&quot;confluence-embedded-image confluence-thumbnail&quot; width=&quot;24&quot; src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177142/preview-button.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1439412514167&amp;amp;api=v2&quot; data-image-src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177142/preview-button.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1439412514167&amp;amp;api=v2&quot;&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;The preview panel is displayed on the right.&lt;br /&gt;You can now click any item that is underlined when you move your mouse pointer over it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;confluence-embedded-image&quot; width=&quot;800&quot; src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177142/diagram-preview-panel.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1439412514112&amp;amp;api=v2&quot; data-image-src=&quot;/download/attachments/13177142/diagram-preview-panel.png?version=1&amp;amp;modificationDate=1439412514112&amp;amp;api=v2&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
    </body>
